verbose_text: However, despite the fact that monocytes are the primary infiltrating cell type, VEGF does not appear to promote monocyte infiltration in ECOR, since (1) VEGF induction is not evident until the inflammation has subsided and (2) VEGF induction is not demonstrated in CD-1 mice despite the fact that the inflammatory response to coronavirus infection in CD-1 mice is even greater than that in BALB/c mice.
evidence: VEGF does not appear to promote monocyte infiltration
